title: Thursday Pt2: Will Eagles remain undefeated? Next destination for OBJ? HOF TE Tony Gonzalez
itunes:title: Thursday Pt2: Will Eagles remain undefeated? Next destination for OBJ? HOF TE Tony Gonzalez
description:
Part Two of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty focusing on the Dallas Cowboys-Philadelphia Eagles matchup on Sunday Night Football, with everyone sharing how the Eagles can remain undefeated. Next, the GMFB panel shares which team Odell Beckham Jr. should sign with and then they’re joined by HOF TE Tony Gonzalez and he talks about the development of Justin Fields and Kyle Pitts and Travis Kelce’s unique ability.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
